---
layout: base-layout.njk
pagination:
  data: collections.post
  size: 10
  reverse: true
  alias: posts
---
<p class="intro-paragraph">I'm a front end developer, web accessibility advocate, and sentient cloud of nanomachines.</p>
<p class="intro-paragraph">This is an archive of my non-performative writing. Stuff I want to remember and maybe share with other people.</p>
{% for post in posts %}
  <article>
    <h2 class="article-title">
      <a href="{{ post.url | url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
    </h2>
    <time datetime="{{ post.date | dateIso }}">{{ post.date | dateReadable }}</time>
  </article>
{% endfor %}
